column1: This Thanksgiving I am  🌻 Thankful for all of the people who voted & volunteered their time and effort to make a difference in our community  🌾 grateful for the opportunity to move our country forward  🍂 and honored to continue representing #TX07.  #HappyThanksgiving! https://t.co/KpEAiwbeAF
Happy #Diwali and Sal Mubarak to all who are celebrating in #TX07 and everywhere!

So glad to see this morning that @JoeBiden and @KamalaHarris are projected winners of this historic presidential election.  This is our democracy at work. And I know that they will work to serve all of us and bring all of us together for the good of our entire country.

We did it! Thanks to all who voted volunteered and gave so much to win #TX07 again.   In Houston we work together to make this a better place for all—and I look forward to bringing that spirit with me back to Washington for the 117th Congress! https://t.co/TktYvDk8K2
